data.description: Motivated Seller! Seasonal Mountain View Chalet style home located in the Sky Hawk Mountain Development. This 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home with the master suite on the main floor has been remodeled, updated and refreshed! Featuring bamboo wood floors on the main level, new cabinetry, countertops and appliances. This home has a welcoming atmosphere and the back porch is perfect for overlooking the seasonal view and enjoying the fresh mountain air. The backyard is spacious and perfect for gardening with the fruit trees already in place. Located close to Boundary Waters Marina, Lake Chatuge Recreational Area, Downtown Hiawassee, Shopping, Restaurants, Golfing and the Georgia Mountain Fairgrounds. This is the perfect mountain escape and it is ready for you to make it your own! Call today to schedule a showing! Seller has an Assumable FHA Loan!
